Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.64,0:00:59.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.60,0:01:02.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,东西被人抢走了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.72,0:01:05.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？那剑柄呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.95,0:01:06.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.98,0:01:09.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要让对方先采取行动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.92,0:01:12.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去把东西抢回来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.78,0:01:15.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮我转告大人一声
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.95,0:01:16.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.66,0:01:20.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动作要快才行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.11,0:01:31.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快刀乱麻 上卷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.16,0:01:37.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新十郎…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.46,0:01:41.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新十郎 快起来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.40,0:01:42.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新十郎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.66,0:01:50.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安 淑乃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.68,0:01:53.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大事不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.28,0:01:55.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铁舟斋大人送了这个过来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.30,0:02:00.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给新十郎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.06,0:02:03.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要出去旅行一段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.14,0:02:06.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以决定把道场让给你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.45,0:02:07.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你带领他们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.86,0:02:09.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好加油
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.12,0:02:13.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铁舟斋大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.20,0:02:14.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.40,0:02:19.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们也不需要马上退出啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.84,0:02:23.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是因为崇拜老师
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.64,0:02:25.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才加入他的门下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.14,0:02:27.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在老师突然说要退休
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.48,0:02:29.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我无法接受
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.10,0:02:32.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更何况新十郎还年轻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.88,0:02:35.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然他是老师的儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.82,0:02:37.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我不认为他能领导道场
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.32,0:02:40.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之我们要退出
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.16,0:02:47.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法啦 淑乃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.84,0:02:50.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我果然没办法让人产生信赖感
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.28,0:02:54.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是这一点不好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.12,0:02:57.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你对自己要有信心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.64,0:03:02.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.11,0:03:05.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一副很生气的样子走掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.78,0:03:07.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生了什么事啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.22,0:03:09.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是小春啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.16,0:03:10.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.64,0:03:12.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.45,0:03:17.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？新十郎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.11,0:03:18.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.74,0:03:22.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才大家都说要退出道场
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.42,0:03:24.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再这样下去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.00,0:03:26.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,道场会倒闭的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.14,0:03:28.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎么办才好…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.64,0:03:33.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 我和你们一起住怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.82,0:03:36.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正想一个人独自生活看看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.24,0:03:40.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想爸爸一定能体谅我的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.78,0:03:41.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.90,0:03:44.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.44,0:03:47.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也会付房租的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.52,0:03:49.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好不好嘛 淑乃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.52,0:03:51.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.80,0:03:52.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.48,0:03:54.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.32,0:03:57.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只到铁舟斋大人回来为止喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.03,0:03:59.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.56,0:04:02.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我马上叫人把行李送过来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.06,0:04:04.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.08,0:04:07.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊 正所谓好事不宜迟嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.78,0:04:13.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,淑乃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.95,0:04:15.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.45,0:04:19.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维持一个道场很难的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.40,0:04:20.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.10,0:04:22.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外头有客人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.02,0:04:23.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.61,0:04:32.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.66,0:04:35.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫丽琳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.32,0:04:38.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问铁舟斋老师在吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.61,0:04:41.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 他出远门
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.42,0:04:42.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过一段时间才会回来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.66,0:04:46.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人家大老远从中国跑来的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.78,0:04:48.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中国？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.32,0:04:52.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你是龙先生的千金？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.04,0:04:56.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是代替爸爸来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.68,0:04:57.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.42,0:05:01.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师曾说他去中国修练的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.16,0:05:05.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,经常受到这个人的帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.16,0:05:08.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.16,0:05:11.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.04,0:05:14.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是他儿子 我叫新十郎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.42,0:05:20.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.98,0:05:22.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在老师回来之前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.64,0:05:24.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就住在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.58,0:05:27.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是不知道他什么时候回来喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.03,0:05:28.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.98,0:05:30.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正我还有其它的事要办
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.80,0:05:35.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话 那我呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.70,0:05:38.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伤脑筋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.42,0:05:41.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有一间空房
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.98,0:05:43.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.30,0:05:46.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.86,0:05:49.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽琳睡新十郎的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.16,0:05:51.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么！?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.70,0:05:55.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行！绝对不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.26,0:05:57.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.96,0:06:00.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你跟新十郎是什么关系？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.12,0:06:04.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是…只是青梅竹马
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.42,0:06:07.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你有什么资格说话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.14,0:06:09.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.62,0:06:11.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.06,0:06:14.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小春你跟我一起睡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.36,0:06:16.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.40,0:06:19.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也会准备丽琳的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.22,0:06:21.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样应该没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.78,0:06:23.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.46,0:06:29.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是奉行所派来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.18,0:06:34.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在正向各个道场征求深夜巡逻的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.95,0:06:36.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深夜巡逻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.38,0:06:49.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好冷喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.66,0:06:53.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才叫你别跟来呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.02,0:06:56.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人家行李又还没到 闲着也是闲着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.06,0:06:59.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就回去看看嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.44,0:07:01.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.42,0:07:04.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爸一定不会让我来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.61,0:07:05.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.12,0:07:07.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是说他会体谅你吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.11,0:07:09.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.95,0:07:13.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是他唯一的独生女耶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.45,0:07:16.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁叫他老是这么啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.06,0:07:18.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好…好狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.95,0:07:22.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕 火熄掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.95,0:07:28.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 快点点着啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.28,0:07:33.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新十郎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.80,0:07:37.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.11,0:07:43.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是盗贼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.88,0:07:46.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小春你待在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.98,0:07:48.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别太勉强喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.00,0:07:56.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.95,0:08:01.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是盗贼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.52,0:08:49.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女…女的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.40,0:08:57.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新十郎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.46,0:09:01.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新十郎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.28,0:09:04.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.45,0:09:07.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.88,0:09:17.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟丢了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.11,0:09:19.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该还在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.18,0:09:21.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.64,0:09:22.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.11,0:09:27.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在下是修平寺的炎罗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.68,0:09:31.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在找一伙盗贼吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.38,0:09:33.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.04,0:09:35.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才看到盗贼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.82,0:09:39.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来就交给我们修平寺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.78,0:09:42.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为事关我们的面子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.80,0:09:46.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 现在还讲什么面子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.84,0:09:51.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更何况他受了伤 这样是抓不到盗贼的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.45,0:10:01.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.04,0:10:06.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 新十郎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.02,0:10:13.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就麻烦您了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.06,0:10:21.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,楯冈新十郎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.00,0:10:28.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然在这么有趣的地方见面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.95,0:10:30.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你介意吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.24,0:10:32.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,介意的人是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.12,0:10:38.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活人剑啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.70,0:10:52.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.28,0:11:00.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是小春和新十郎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.00,0:11:03.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么晚了 有什么事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.45,0:11:06.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你帮新十郎治疗一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.64,0:11:10.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么严重？要快点治疗才行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.20,0:11:12.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快 快进来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.64,0:11:18.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 这么晚来打扰你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.95,0:11:22.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.28,0:11:26.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 包好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.00,0:11:28.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 纱奈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.48,0:11:31.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是好可惜喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.66,0:11:33.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差一点点就可以抓到的说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.45,0:11:36.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.36,0:11:39.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能从新十郎手上逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.18,0:11:42.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是很强的盗贼啰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.78,0:11:44.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.28,0:11:46.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不是太大意了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.78,0:11:48.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.10,0:11:50.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对方是女生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.10,0:11:52.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.06,0:12:02.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.16,0:12:04.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女人的胸部…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.34,0:12:07.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摸起来很软耶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.61,0:12:10.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.32,0:12:15.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样 才会被她砍了一刀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.78,0:12:19.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我吓了一跳嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.36,0:12:25.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还笑得出来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.00,0:12:29.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亏人家还那么为你担心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.14,0:12:33.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新十郎你这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.61,0:12:35.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.14,0:12:38.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我…我又不是故意的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.92,0:12:40.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还敢狡辩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.26,0:12:44.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊...气死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.76,0:12:46.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新十郎你这个混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.08,0:12:43.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(309.969,42)}小春你别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.16,0:12:44.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(309.969,42)}别…别…别这样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.03,0:12:55.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我黏 我黏 我黏黏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.86,0:13:00.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于黏好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.88,0:13:02.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟 纱奈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.60,0:13:05.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是美怜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.03,0:13:07.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.42,0:13:08.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,贴纸门
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.03,0:13:12.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要重贴呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.36,0:13:15.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨晚小春…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.86,0:13:17.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她又发飙了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.20,0:13:19.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.12,0:13:22.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新十郎好可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.86,0:13:26.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新十郎他怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.06,0:13:30.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.02,0:13:38.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.10,0:13:43.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 小春
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.24,0:13:47.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是美怜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.36,0:13:49.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见了 美怜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.38,0:13:51.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么跑来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.20,0:13:55.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想问问你昨晚的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.36,0:14:02.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新…新十郎你呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.03,0:14:04.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是飞来横祸哪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.28,0:14:08.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她突然就一拳过来了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.70,0:14:09.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.46,0:14:12.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过就我从纱奈那里听到的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.32,0:14:14.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是你摸到小春的胸部耶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.36,0:14:17.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别开这种玩笑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.70,0:14:19.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.82,0:14:21.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我摸胸部也会选的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.70,0:14:25.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.48,0:14:26.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.08,0:14:29.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天小春也会变大的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.94,0:14:31.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像我一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.20,0:14:42.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 新十郎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.86,0:14:44.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟那个女的比起来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.86,0:14:47.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁比较大 你比比看嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.86,0:14:51.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 这…这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.14,0:14:53.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点嘛 新十郎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.14,0:14:57.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不摸怎么比得出来嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.70,0:15:03.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那一下下就好…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.86,0:15:08.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新十郎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.20,0:15:11.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.36,0:15:13.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是开玩笑的 开玩笑的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.76,0:15:15.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想装蒜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.36,0:15:18.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,气死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.42,0:15:19.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.70,0:15:22.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阻止你追下去的那个武士
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.20,0:15:23.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是何方神圣啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.70,0:15:28.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得他说他是修平寺的 名字叫做炎罗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.36,0:15:30.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修平寺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.44,0:15:32.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.42,0:15:36.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一年前成立的道场
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.60,0:15:39.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主持道场的人叫做御影 似乎蛮有一套的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.58,0:15:45.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茶来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.10,0:15:47.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.56,0:15:49.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笑得太过火 嘴巴都干了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.20,0:15:51.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 丽琳呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.62,0:15:53.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她刚刚出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.42,0:15:54.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁是丽琳？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.20,0:15:56.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铁舟斋师传的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.78,0:15:58.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.36,0:16:00.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胸部大吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.30,0:16:03.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别再说了啦 美怜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.50,0:16:05.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.84,0:16:07.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美怜你真是的 还闹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.36,0:16:17.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要出去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.88,0:16:21.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伤也好得差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.70,0:16:23.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以想出去散个步
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.08,0:16:25.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.20,0:16:26.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好是好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.32,0:16:29.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过真的只是散步喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.70,0:16:31.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也不错 走吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.30,0:16:39.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 新十郎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.36,0:16:43.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很厉害吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.38,0:16:46.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.53,0:16:48.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜欢剑术吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.20,0:16:54.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算喜欢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.60,0:16:55.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新十郎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.54,0:17:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是楯冈新十郎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.86,0:17:02.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.62,0:17:06.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是修平寺的御影真幌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.06,0:17:08.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是御影…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.80,0:17:10.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.80,0:17:13.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有事想和你谈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.40,0:17:15.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.74,0:17:21.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.03,0:17:24.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.53,0:17:30.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.42,0:17:44.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.22,0:17:48.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我对活人剑相当感兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.22,0:17:51.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身手不错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.18,0:17:53.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.88,0:17:55.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有杀过人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.70,0:17:57.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.76,0:17:58.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我杀过人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.32,0:18:02.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剑这玩意 本来就是用来杀人的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.03,0:18:05.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事实不就是如此吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.60,0:18:08.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活人剑也是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.86,0:18:09.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.36,0:18:12.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.36,0:18:16.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.40,0:18:20.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须和你分出高下也说不定
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.46,0:18:31.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那一瞬间我吓了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.06,0:18:32.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.26,0:18:38.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也有相同的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.46,0:18:54.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来还是得小心行事才行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.53,0:18:55.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.80,0:18:58.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就可以使用神秘之剑了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.92,0:19:02.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到居然少了剑柄 我太大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.86,0:19:05.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是幕府似乎也察觉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.20,0:19:08.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烧掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.03,0:19:10.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是认真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.58,0:19:13.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要走错一步 江户会变成一片火海的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.18,0:19:15.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.28,0:19:17.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正到时候会有人灭火…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.44,0:19:20.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幕府啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.70,0:19:23.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 随你高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.14,0:19:25.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我欠你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.70,0:19:29.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在得神秘之剑以前 我就陪你们玩玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.70,0:19:38.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是密探吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.03,0:19:40.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.62,0:19:42.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来这件事越快越好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.24,0:19:46.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天马上行动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.04,0:20:44.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么又做这个梦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.78,0:20:58.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新十郎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.38,0:21:02.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小春
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.95,0:21:04.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.11,0:21:09.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡不着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.61,0:21:14.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是有什么烦恼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.62,0:21:20.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做了一个梦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.78,0:21:24.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个小时候的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.45,0:21:26.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活人…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.45,0:21:28.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.11,0:21:34.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新十郎…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.04,0:21:39.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提起精神来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.45,0:21:41.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也对
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.78,0:21:43.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.86,0:21:44.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.78,0:21:54.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得是这附近
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.78,0:21:59.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.40,0:22:10.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽…丽琳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.45,0:22:12.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.28,0:22:15.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她伤得好重
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.86,0:22:17.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去叫淑乃过来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.28,0:22:18.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.78,0:22:35.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 晚上跑出去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.11,0:22:37.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是做什么坏事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.32,0:22:38.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽琳吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.02,0:22:41.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就我看来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.72,0:22:43.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这其中另有内幕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.32,0:22:46.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也有这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.28,0:22:49.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新十郎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.45,0:22:53.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽琳她醒过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.53,0:22:58.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽琳 丽琳
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.86,0:23:07.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新…十…郎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.30,0:23:10.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 你醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.56,0:23:11.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御影…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.36,0:23:17.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修平寺的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.50,0:23:18.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要放火…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.36,0:23:20.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还不能乱动啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.36,0:23:23.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.36,0:23:25.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们要烧了这座城
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.36,0:23:30.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽琳 你到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.53,0:23:31.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.28,0:23:34.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在只能告诉你这些
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.36,0:23:36.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.53,0:23:59.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纱奈 丽琳就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.32,0:24:07.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失火了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.76,0:24:13.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.28,0:24:16.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许还有人来不及逃生
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.03,0:24:18.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 新十郎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.53,0:24:28.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是那时候的…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.03,0:24:44.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们到底想干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.86,0:25:08.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新十郎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.54,0:25:15.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御影
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.86,0:25:19.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么巧啊 新十郎
